0response%20to%20a%20slew%20of%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20Centre's%20move%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20petitioners%20have%20argued%20that%20Article%20370%20cannot%20be%20scrapped%20unilaterally%20by%20the%20Centre%2C%20since%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20was%20vested%20in%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20legislature%20after%20it%20was%20dissolved%20in%201957.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20top%20court%20has%20questioned%20who%20can%20recommend%20the%20revocation%20of%20Article%20370.%20Under%20the%20rules%2C%20a%20nod%20is%20required%20from%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20to%20scrap%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20the%20Constitution%20held%20temporary.%20The%20court%20has%20also%20asked%20how%20the%20Article%20became%20permanent%20after%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20was%20dissolved.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20argued%20that%20its%20decisions%20were%20taken%20within%20the%20legal%20framework.%20It%20has%20also%20contended%20that%20the%20mainstreaming%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20reduced%20terrorism%20and%20provided%20a%20level%20playing%20field.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOver%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20it%20has%20helped%20move%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20on%20the%20fast-track%20to%20development%2C%20the%20government%20has%20argued.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EArticle%20370%2C%20it%20also%20maintained%2C%20deprived%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20of%20many%20fundamental%20rights%2C%20including%20the%20right%20to%20education.%20The%20Constitutional%20rights%20that%20automatically%20apply%20to%20every%20Indian%20could%20not%20apply%20to%20residents%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20unless%20okayed%20by%20the%20state%20legislature.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EConversely%2C%20Article%2035A%2C%20which%20was%20also%20scrapped%20along%20with%20Article%20370%2C%20did%20not%20allow%20people%20from%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20the%20right%20to%20get%20jobs%2C%20own%20land%20and%20settle%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20--%20which%20is%20part%20of%20their%20fundamental%20rights.%20These%20were%20reserved%20as%20special%20privileges%20reserved%20only%20for%20the%20residents%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESecurity%20has%20been%20strengthened%20in%20Kashmir%20Valley%20ahead%20of%20the%20verdict.%20The%20BJP%20has%20said%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20top%20court%20should%20be%20respected.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFormer%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20National%20Conference%20chief%20Omar%20Abdullah%20said%20his%20party%20will%20not%20disturb%20the%20peace%20even%20in%20case%20of%20an%20adverse%20verdict.%20They%20will%20continue%20their%20fight%20in%20a%20lawful%20manner%2C%20he%20said.%20Mehbooba%20Mufti's%20People'%20Democratic%20Party%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20expressed%20hope%20that%20the%20court%20will%20be%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EArticle%20370%20was%20scrapped%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20split%20in%20August%202019%20-%20over%20a%20year%20after%20the%20PDP-BJP%20alliance%20government%20had%20collapsed%20.%20It%20took%20place%20while%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20was%20under%20President's%20Rule.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702256220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%2Fa1ooga8_supreme-court-of-india_650x400_14_February_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farticle-370-supreme-court-verdict-on-validity-of-ending-j-k-special-status-today-4652198%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Was%20the%20Centre's%20move%20to%20scrap%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20Constitution%20that%20gave%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20its%20special%20status%20and%20split%20the%20state%20into%20two%20Union%20Territories%2C%20constitutionally%20valid%3F%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20a%20call%20on%20the%20issue%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia