.%20Flat%20rice%20noodles%20near%20two%20of%20Hanoi's%20most%20storied%20streets%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20sitting%20on%20stools%20in%20Hanoi%20eating%20street%20food.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570039758e7c0c29a29fd50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPh%E1%BB%9F%20H%E1%BA%A1nh%20is%20near%20the%20corner%20of%20two%20of%20Hanoi's%20most%20storied%20streets.%3Cp%3EJoshua%20Zukas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20visitors%20leave%20Vietnam%20thinking%20that%20ph%E1%BB%9F%20is%20noodle%20soup%2C%20when%20the%20word%20actually%20refers%20to%20a%20repertoire%20of%20dishes.%20One%20is%20ph%E1%BB%9F%20tr%E1%BB%99n%2C%20a%20broth-less%20bowl%20of%20flat%20rice%20noodles%20topped%20with%20meat%2C%20deep-fried%20shallots%2C%20peanuts%2C%20greens%2C%20and%20a%20sweetened%20fish%20sauce.%20Dine%20on%20the%20chicken%20version%20of%20this%20dish%2C%20which%20isn't%20featured%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmichelin-star-auntie-lean-gaik-review-penang-malaysia-menu-prices-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMichelin%20Guide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20at%20Ph%E1%BB%9F%20H%E1%BA%A1nh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPh%E1%BB%9F%20H%E1%BA%A1nh%20is%20near%20the%20corner%20of%20two%20of%20Hanoi's%20most%20storied%20streets%3A%20Thu%E1%BB%91c%20B%E1%BA%AFc%20and%20L%C3%A3n%20%C3%94ng.%20Thu%E1%BB%91c%20B%E1%BA%AFc%20means%20%26quot%3Bnorthern%20(or%20Chinese)%20medicine%26quot%3B%20and%20L%C3%A3n%20%C3%94ng%20means%20%26quot%3Blazy%20old%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20named%20after%20a%20sluggish%20but%20prodigal%2018th-century%20doctor%20who%20lived%20and%20practiced%20in%20the%20area.%20These%20are%20some%20of%20the%20only%20streets%20in%20Hanoi's%20Old%20Quarter%20that%20still%20sell%20the%20type%20of%20products%20that%20the%20streets%20were%20originally%20named%20after.%20As%20you%20slurp%20up%20noodles%2C%20the%20scents%20of%20