22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fpolitics%2F2023%2F12%2F10%2Ftrump-fake-electors-charges%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20wouldn't%20do%20it%20again.%20Some%20of%20the%20electors%20are%20now%20entangled%20in%20criminal%20probes%20and%20could%20face%20criminal%20charges%2C%20with%20mounting%20legal%20expenses%20also%20adding%20to%20their%20worries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202020%2C%20Republican%20activist%20James%20%26quot%3BKen%26quot%3B%20Carroll%20cast%20an%20electoral%20vote%20for%20Trump%20at%20the%20Georgia%20State%20Capitol%20in%20Atlanta%20as%20part%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Balternate%26quot%3B%20slate%20of%20delegates%2C%20despite%20Biden's%20certified%20victory%20in%20the%20former%20Republican%20stronghold-turned-swing%20state.%20He%20was%20one%20of%2016%20GOP%20signatories%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Carroll%20told%20The%20Post%20that%20he%20wouldn't%20take%20the%20same%20action%20if%20he%20could%20go%20back%20in%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKnowing%20what%20I%20know%20now%3F%20No%2C%26quot%3B%20Carroll%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20hindsight%20provides%20a%20wealth%20of%20knowledge%20we%20don't%20have%20at%20the%20time%20of%20an%20event.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%2025%20of%20the%2084%20electors%20involved%20in%20alternate%20elector%20schemes%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20a%20series%20of%20felonies%2C%20and%2010%20additional%20electors%20have%20agreed%20not%20to%20put%20their%20names%20forward%20as%20legitimate%20electors%20in%20any%20election%20featuring%20Trump%20on%20the%20ballot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Arizona%2C%20Georgia%2C%20Michigan%2C%20Nevada%2C%20New%20Mexico%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20and%20Wisconsin%2C%20fake%20electors%20sought%20to%20overturn%20the%20election%20by%20filing%20paperwork%20stating%20that%20it%20was%20Trump%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20Biden%20%E2%80%94%20who%20had%20truly%20won%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C