upcoming%20film%20Kho%20Gaye%20Hum%20Kahan%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Ananya%20Panday%20gave%20a%20piece%20of%20advice%20on%20how%20to%20move%20on%20post%20breaking%20up%20amid%20dating%20rumours%20with%20Aditya%20Roy%20Kapur.%20She%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20move%20on%20too%20fast.%20Go%20through%20it.%20Eat%20ice%20cream.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Famid-dating-rumours-with-aditya-roy-kapur-ananya-panday-gives-a-piece-of-advice-on-how-to-move-on-post-breaking-up%2Farticleshow%2F105883865.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20agency%20proposes%20shooting%20dead%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20owls%20of%20one%20kind%20to%20save%20owls%20of%20another%20kind%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20juvenile%20barred%20owls.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657601ae0ec98e92f74df2c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20juvenile%20barred%20owls%20in%20a%20tree%20in%20Washington%20state.%3Cp%3EWolfgang%20Kaehler%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20Fish%20and%20Wildlife%20Service%20proposes%20killing%20thousands%20of%20one%20owl%20species%20to%20preserve%20another.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20invasive%20barred%20owls%20are%20threatening%20native%20spotted%20owls%2C%20the%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20service%20suggests%20eliminating%2020%2C000%20to%2046%2C000%20barred%20owls%20in%20a%20single%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Fish%20and%20Wildlife%20Service%20has%20a%20strategy%20for%20owl%20preservation%3A%20kill%20some%20to%20safeguard%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agency's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fws.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fdocuments%2FFinal%2520draft%2520Barred%2520Owl%2520EIS.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproposal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20open%20for%20public%20commentary%20until%20early%202024%2C%20seeks%20to%20preserve%20the%20native%20population%20of%20northern%20spotted%20owls%20and%20California%20spotted%20owls.%20To%20do%20that%2C%20the%20agency%20suggests%20%26quot%3Blethally%20removing%20barred%20owls%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20course%20of%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompetition%20from%20the%20non-native%20invasive%20barred%20owls%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20a%20primary%20threat%20to%20the%20northern%20spotted%20owl%20and%20a%20significant%20and%20increasing%20threat%20to%20the%20California%20spotted%20owl%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20proposal%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20barred%20owls%20are%20%26quot%3Bslightly%20larger%20and%20more%20aggressive%26quot%3B%20than%20spotted%20owls%2C%20according%20to%20the%20proposal.%20They%20threaten%20spotted%20owls%20by%20disrupting%20their%20nesting%20and%20competing%20for%20prey%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fws.gov%2Fproject%2Fbarred-owl-management%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BResearchers%20also%20have%20seen%20a%20few%20instances%20of%20barred%20owls%20interbreeding%20with%20or%20killing%20spotted%20owls.%20Because%20the%20spotted%20owl%20is%20already%20struggling%20due%20to%20its%20reduced%20habitat%2C%20the%20effect%20of%20the%20barred%20owl's%20presence%20is%20an%20added%20stressor%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20service%20press%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20has%20a%20variety%20of%20alternatives%20debating%20how%20many%20barred%20owls%20to%20eliminate%2C%20including%20taking%20no%20action%20at%20all.%20Among%20the%20six%20alternatives%20proposed%2C%20the%20numbers%20for%20elimination%20in%20the%20first%20year%20range%20from%20about%200%20to%2020%2C000%20to%2046%2C000%20barred%20owls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20number%20of%20owls%20removed%20over%20three%20decades%20ranges%20from%200%20to%20nearly%2030%2C000%20annually%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20proposed%20alternative%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarred-owls-spotted-owls-conservation-us-fish-wildlife-service-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702233117000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657601cd7a3c8094d5db76b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarred-owls-spotted-owls-conservation-us-fish-wildlife-service-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20proposal%20from%20the%20US%20Fish%20and%20Wildlife%20Service%20suggests%20eliminating%20%26quot%3Blarger%20and%20more%20aggressive%26quot%3B%20barred%20owls%20to%20save%20the%20threatened%20spotted%20owl.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbalevic%40insider.com%20(Katie%20Balevic)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A81%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarred-owls-spotted-owls-conservation-us-fish-wildlife-service-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DK%20Shivakumar%20Offers%20Lok%20Sabha%20Ticket%20To%20Kannada%20Actor%20Shiva%20Rajkumar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%20has%20offered%20a%20ticket%20to%20Kannada%20movie%20star%20Shiva%20Rajkumar%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20'Eidiga'%20community%20convention%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20said%20that%20he%20has%20urged%20Shiva%20Rajkumar%20to%20contest%20from%20%26quot%3Bany%20constituency%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20asked%20Shivraj%20Kumar%20to%20contest%20from%20any%20constituency%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20Karnataka%20as%20it%20is%20a%20great%20op