d%20at%20manned%20aircraft%20and%20drone%20pilots%2C%20combat%20systems%20operators%2C%20and%20air%20battle%20managers%2C%20with%20amounts%20ranging%20from%20%2415%2C000%20to%20%2450%2C000%20per%20year%2C%20depending%20on%20aircraft%20type%20and%20when%20they%20commit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20aims%20to%20retain%20skilled%20airmen%20and%20address%20a%20decades-long%20pilot%20shortage%20that%20has%20affected%20policy-making%20and%20managerial%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFighter%20and%20bomber%20pilots%2C%20as%20well%20as%20mobility%2C%20search-and-rescue%2C%20and%20special%20operations%20pilots%2C%20could%20earn%20%2430%2C000%20to%20%2435%2C000%20a%20year%20on%20three-%20to%20four-year%20contracts%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPilots%20who%20sign%20up%20for%20an%20extra%20five%20to%20seven%20years%20could%20earn%20another%20%2437%2C500%20to%20%2442%2C500%20per%20year%2C%20while%20those%20committing%20to%20eight%20to%2012%20additional%20years%20stand%20to%20earn%20%2445%2C000%20to%20%2450%2C000%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirmen%20operating%20command-and-control%20and%20intelligence%20aircraft%20also%20qualify%20for%20the%20bonuses%20and%20could%20get%20annual%20payments%20of%20%2430%2C000%20to%20%2435%2C000%20over%20three%20to%2012%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20pilots%20opting%20for%20an%20additional%20five%20to%2012%20years%20may%20receive%20a%20lump%20sum%20payment%20of%20up%20to%20%24200%2C000%20upfront.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20initiative%2C%20which%20will%20run%20until%20the%20end%20of%202028%2C%20will%20supplement%20non-financial%20incentives%20offered%20by%20the%20USAF%20to%20those%20in%20the%20demo%2C%20such%20as%20giving%20troops%20more%20of%20a%20say%20over%20where%20they%20are%20based%20and%20what%20assignments%20they%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20data%20indicates%20a%20positive%20response%20to%20the%20demo%20program%2C%20with%20210%20contract%20extensions%20signed%20in%20the%20first%2010%20days%2C%20service%20spokesperson%20Master%20Sgt.%20Deana%20Heitzman%20said%2C%20per%20the%20Air%20Force%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airforcetimes.com%2Fnews%2Fyour-air-force%2F2023%2F09%2F11%2Fair-force-to-fall-nearly-150-pilots-short-of-annual-training-goal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUSAF%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20September%20that%20it%20had%20missed%20its%20annual%20target%20of%20around%201%2C500%20new%20pilots%20for%20the%20eighth%20year%20in%20a%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Air%20Force%20Times%2C%20staffing%20issues%2C%20maintenance%20problems%2C%20and%20unexpected%20setbacks%20meant%20the%20force%20decided%20to%20limit%20its%20training%20numbers%20to%201%2C350%20airmen%20rather%20than%20the%20planned%201%2C470.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20try%20to%20make%20sure%20we%20are%20still%20flying%20because%20that's%20what%20we%20do%20as%20an%20Air%20Force%2C%26quot%3B%20Maj.%20Gen.%20Clark%20Quinn%2C%20the%20general%20in%20charge%20of%20pilot%20training%20told%20reporters%2C%20per%20the%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-air-force-offering-pilot-shortage-retention-bonuses-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702232456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6575e4a258e7c0c29a2b764f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-air-force-offering-pilot-shortage-retention-bonuses-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20USAF%20said%20in%20September%20that%20it%20had%20missed%20its%20annual%20target%20of%20around%201%2C500%20new%20pilots%20for%20the%20eighth%20year%20in%20a%20row.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A112%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-air-force-offering-pilot-shortage-retention-bonuses-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cash%20Haul%20Linked%20To%20Congress%20MP%20Crosses%20Rs%20351%20Crore%2C%20Counting%20Still%20On%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20cash%20seizure%20in%20the%20income-tax%20department's%20searches%20against%20an%20Odisha-based%20distillery%20company%2C%20owned%20by%20a%20Congress%20MP's%20family%2C%20has%20been%20calculated%20at%20Rs%20351%20crore%20after%20five%20days%20of%20counting%20and%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bhighest-ever%26quot%3B%20haul%20in%20a%20single%20action%20by%20any%20probe%20agency%20in%20the%20country%2C%20official%20sources%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20premises%20of%20the%20Congress%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Jharkhand%2C%20Dhiraj%20Prasad%20Sahu%2C%20in%20Ranchi%20and%20other%20places%2C%20were%20also%20covered%20during%20the%20searches%20by%20the%20department.%20The%20company%20and%20the%20member%20of%20Parliament%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20PTI's%20queries%20regarding%20the%20action%20being%20carried%20out%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20marathon%20raids%20against%20Boudh%20Distillery%20Private%20Limited%2C%20its%20promoters%20and%20others%20entered%20the%20fifth%20day%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20raids%20were%20launched%20on%20December%206%20by%20the%20taxman%20on%20charges%20of%20tax%20evasion%20and%20%26quot%3Boff-the-book%26quot%3B%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20told%20PTI%20that%20Rs%20351%20crore%20cash%20has%20been%20counted%20and%20the%20process%20has%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counting%20involved%20nine%20teams%20of%20about%2080%20people%20from%20the%20tax%20department%20and%20various%20banks%2C%20working%20in%20shifts%20in%20a%2024x7%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20team%20of%20200%20officials%2C%20including%20security%20personnel%2C%20drivers%20and%20other%20staff%2C%20joined%20in%20after%20the%20taxman%20found%2010%20almirahs%20stuffed%20with%20cash%20apart%20from%20some%20other%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%20200%20bags%20and%20trunks%20were%20used%20to%20transport%20the%20cash%20for%20depositing%20it%20in%20various%20bank%20branches%20in%20Odisha%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20believes%20that%20the%20entire%20cache%20of%20currency%20is%20%26quot%3Bunaccounted%26quot%3B%20money%20earned%20from%20cash%20sales%20of%20country%20liquor%20by%20the%20business%20group%2C%20distributors%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20highest-ever%20cash%20seizure%20made%20by%20an%20agency%20in%20the%20country%20as%20part%20of%20an%20action%20against%20a%20single%20group%20and%20entities%20linked%20to%20it%2C%20the%20sources%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20high-value%20seizures%20in%20the%20past%20include%20one%20from%202019%20when%20the%20GST%20Intelligence%20raided%20a%20Kanpur-based%20businessman%20and%20seized%20cash%20amounting%20to%20Rs%20257%20crore%20and%20another%20instance%20where%20cash%20amounting%20to%20Rs%20163%20crore%20was%20unearthed%20by%20the%20I-T%20department%20during%20searches%20against%20a%20road%20construction%20firm%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20July%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20is%20also%20recording%20the%20statements%20of%20the%20executives%20and%20other%20staff%20who%20were%20present%20at%20the%20searched%20locations%20and%20will%20soon%20issue%20summonses%20to%20the%20main%20promoters%20of%20the%20company%20for%20recording%20their%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20clear%20what%20amount%20of%20cash%20and%20other%20documents%20were%20seized%20from%20Mr%20Sahu's%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20maximum%20cache%20of%20currency%2C%20largely%20in%20Rs%20500%20denomination%2C%20was%20recovered%20from%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20company%20in%20Bolangir%20district%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20on%20Sunday%20stepped%20up%20its%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20opposition%20parties%2C%20with%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20