c.twitter.com%2F2esDCyip1O%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Amit%20Malviya%20(%40amitmalviya)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Famitmalviya%2Fstatus%2F1733751877219848553%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2010%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20post%2C%20BJP's%20IT%20Cell%20chief%20Amit%20Malviya%20wrote%20Mr%20Sahu%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bdark%20sense%20of%20humour%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20hashtag%20%26quot%3Bcorruption%20ki%20dukaan%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20Rs%20290%20crore%20was%20seized%20in%20cash%20during%20raids%20on%20the%20offices%20of%20an%20Odisha-based%20distillery%20and%20entities%20linked%20to%20it%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20Bengal.%20The%20distillery%20is%20linked%20to%20Dheeraj%20Sahu%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Income%20Tax%20raids%20on%20the%20premises%20of%20Boudh%20Distilleries%20Private%20Limited%20entered%20its%20fifth%20day%20today.%20More%20cash%20counting%20machines%20were%20brought%20into%20the%20premises%20of%20Boudh%20Distilleries%20linked%20to%20Dheeraj%20Sahu%20today.%20Earlier%2C%20officials%20had%20swooped%20in%20on%20the%20MP's%20residences%20in%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFacing%20massive%20flak%20over%20the%20whopping%20amounts%20of%20hard%20cash%20recovered%20in%20what%20is%20touted%20as%20one%20of%20India's%20biggest%20cash%20hauls%2C%20the%20Congress%20on%20Saturday%20distanced%20itself%20from%20its%20MP%20and%20said%20that%20it%20is%20not%20connected%20with%20the%20businesses%20in%20any%20way%20and%20that%20the%20MP%20should%20explain%20the%20cash%20and%20its%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20launched%20an%20all-out%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress%20over%20the%20recovery%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20leading%20the%20party's%20charge%20against%20the%20Congress.%20On%20X%2C%20the%20PM%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20the%20country%20should%20look%20atthese%20piles%20of%20currency%20notes%20and%20then%20listen%20to%20the%20honest%20'speeches'%20of%20their%20leaders...%20Whatever%20has%20been%20looted%20from%20the%20public%2C%20every%20penny%20will%20have%20to%20be%20returned.%20This%20is%20Modi's%20guarantee.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20questioned%20the%20Congress%20and%20said%20that%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20must%20reveal%20the%20name%20of%20the%20leader%20for%20whom%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20was%20working%20as%20an%20%26quot%3BATM%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20Odisha%20unit%20has%20demanded%20a%20probe%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20and%20sought%20clarification%20from%20the%20ruling%20BJD.%20Party%20spokesperson%20Manoj%20Mohapatra%20showed%20photos%20of%20a%20woman%20minister%20from%20the%20state%20sharing%20stage%20with%20one%20of%20the%20liquor%20traders%20covered%20in%20the%20raids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20tax%20evasion%20could%20not%20have%20been%20possible%20without%20the%20active%20support%20and%20patronage%20of%20local%20leaders%20and%20the%20state%20government%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702224360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fji0boflk_dheeraj-sahu-1200_625x300_10_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-mp-dheeraj-sahu-2022-post-black-money-is-viral-crores-seized-from-him-4651552%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20seemingly%20harmless%202022%20post%20on%20X%20about%20rampant%20corruption%20and%20the%20extensive%20circulation%20of%20black%20money%20is%20being%20shared%20widely%20on%20social%20media%20and%20is%20now%20viral.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-mp-dheeraj-sahu-2022-post-black-money-is-viral-crores-seized-from-him-4651552%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%