0Court%20observed%20that%20%26quot%3Bprotection%20of%20a%20person%26quot%3B%20from%20being%20charged%20in%20%26quot%3Bmarital%20rape%20continues%20in%20cases%20where%20the%20wife%20is%20of%2018%20years%20of%20age%20or%20more%26quot%3B.%20The%20court%20also%20cited%20the%20judgment%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Independent%20Thought%20Vs%20Union%20of%20India%20(2017)%20where%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20held%20that%20any%20sexual%20intercourse%20between%20a%20man%20and%20his%20wife%20aged%20between%2015%20to%2018%20years%20would%20amount%20to%20rape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Ram%20Manohar%20Narayan%20Mishra%2C%20while%20acquitting%20a%20husband%20under%20section%20377%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20for%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bunnatural%20sex%26quot%3B%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20noted%20that%20%26quot%3Bingredients%20of%20unnatural%20sex%2C%20comprised%20under%20Section%20377%20IPC%20are%20included%20in%20Section%20375%20(a)%20IPC%20as%20observed%20by%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%2C%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20had%20opined%20that%20Section%20375%20IPC%20related%20to%20rape%20(as%20amended%20by%20the%202013%20Amendment%20Act)%20includes%20all%20possible%20parts%20of%20penetration%20of%20the%20penis.%20When%20consent%20for%20such%20an%20act%20is%20immaterial%2C%20then%20there%20is%20no%20scope%20for%20the%20offence%20of%20Section%20377%20IPC%20to%20get%20attracted%20where%20husband%20and%20wife%20are%20involved%20in%20sexual%20acts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThus%2C%20on%20perusal%20of%20aforesaid%20judgement%20also%20it%20appears%20that%20protection%20of%20a%20person%20from%20marital%20rape%20still%20continues%20in%20the%20case%20where%20the%20wife%20is%20of%2018%20years%20of%20age%20or%20more%20than%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20partly%20allowing%20a%20revision%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20accused%2C%20Justice%20Ram%20Manohar%20Narayan%20Mishra%20noted%20that%20in%20the%20proposed%20Bhartiya%20Nyay%20Sanhita%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20there%20is%20no%20provision%20of%20377%20of%20IPC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20however%2C%20affirmed%20his%20conviction%20and%20sentence%20for%20charges%20under%20section%20498A%20(harassment%20for%20dowry)%20and%20323%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20against%20the%20man%20under%20sections%20498A%2C%20323%2C%20504%20and%20377%20of%20IPC%20and%20also%20under%20the%20Dowry%20Prohibition%20Act%20in%20Ghaziabad.%20The%20trial%20court%20at%20Ghaziabad%20convicted%20him%20and%20the%20appellate%20court%20also%20upheld%20the%20findings%20after%20which%20he%20moved%20the%20revision%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20noted%20that%20there%20was%20no%20factual%20or%20legal%20error%20in%20the%20finding%20of%20guilt%20recorded%20by%20the%20appellate%20court%20as%20regards%20the%20charge%20under%20section%20323%2C%20498-A%20IPC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20certain%20petitions%20are%20pending%20for%20consideration%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20criminalising%20marital%20rape%2C%20but%20till%20any%20decision%20comes%20on%20those%20petitions%2C%20the%20court%20added%2C%20there%20is%20no%20criminal%20penalty%20for%20such%20acts%20when%20the%20wife%20is%20of%20or%20above%2018%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20noting%20that%20the%20medical%20evidence%20in%20the%20case%20was%20not%20supportive%20of%20allegations%20of%20commission%20of%20unnatural%20sex%2C%20the%20court%20in%20this%20judgment%20dated%20December%206%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20proposed%20Bhartiya%20Nyay%20Sanhita%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20replace%20IPC%2C%20no%20provision%20like%20Section%20377%20IPC%20is%20included%20therein.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20charge%20of%20committing%20matrimonial%20cruelty%20against%20the%20revisionist%20is%20proved%20in%20this%20case%20and%20the%20same%20is%20corroborated%20by%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20family%20court%20while%20decreeing%20the%20divorce%20petition%20and%20this%20court%20in%20appeal%20while%20affirming%20the%20decree%20of%20divorce%20against%20the%20revisionist%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702219980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-01%2F7eom9oh8_allahabad-high-court-ndtv_625x300_07_January_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-cant-be-charged-with-marital-rape-if-wife-is-18-or-above-allahabad-high-court-4651429%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20observed%20that%20%26quot%3Bprotection%20of%20a%20person%26quot%3B%20from%20being%20charged%20in%20%26quot%3Bmarital%20rape%20continues%20in%20cases%20where%20the%20wife%20is%20of%2018%20years%20of%20age%20or%20more%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-cant-be-charged-with-marital-rape-if-wife-is-18-or-above-allahabad-high-court-4651429%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-cant-be-charged-with-marital-rape-if-wife-is-18-or-above-allahabad-high-court-4651429%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-cant-be-charged-with-marital-rape-if-wife-is-18-or-above-allahabad-high-court-4651429%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mortgage%20firm%20SRG%20Housing%20Finance%20aims%20to%20hit%20Rs%20750%20cr%20AUM%20next%20fiscal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702219823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticl