%2Farticleshow%2F100450885.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findia-extends-restrictions-on-sugar-exports-until-further-orders-11697611475899.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epolicy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Findia-bans-onion-exports-till-march-next-year%2Farticleshow%2F105829256.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eactions%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20centred%20on%20agricultural%20crops%2C%20two%20things%20(among%20many%20others)%20come%20out%20clear%3A%20(i)%20domestic%20food%20security%20is%20central%20to%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20even%20above%20other%20priorities%20including%20energy%20security%3B%20and%20that%20(ii)%20two%20years%20of%20consecutive%20shocks%20from%20climate%20(high%20temperatures%20and%20sub-optimal%20rains)%20have%20turned%20tables%20of%20a%20food%20surplus%20nation%20into%20one%20which%20is%20scratching%20to%20achieve%20self-sufficiency.%20In%20this%20brief%20article%2C%20we%20analyse%20recent%20government%20decision%20on%20ethanol%20and%20how%20El%20Ni%C3%B1o%20and%20high%20temperatures%20may%20have%20derailed%20country%E2%80%99s%20E20%20action%20plans%2C%20hopefully%20for%20a%20short%20period%20only.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20December%207%20decision%20regarding%20use%20of%20molasses%20for%20ethanol%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdfpd.gov.in%2FLwB3AHIAaQB0AGUAcgBlAGEAZABkAGEAdABhAC8AUABvAHIAdABhAGwALwBOAGUAdwBzAC8A745_1_Supply_of_ethanol_from_sugar_and_molasses_based_distilleries.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eletter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20Indian%20sugar%20mills%20and%20distilleries%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Food%20and%20Public%20Distribution%20(DFPD)%2C%20which%20is%20the%20nodal%20agency%20for%20sugar%20policies%20in%20India%2C%20invoked%20provisions%20of%20the%20Essential%20Commodities%20Act%2C%201955%20(ECA)%20to%20direct%20two%20changes%3A%20(i)%20ban%20use%20of%20sugarcane%20juice%20and%20syrup%20for%20ethanol%20production%3B%20and%20(ii)%20restrict%20ethanol%20produced%20from%20B-heavy%20molasses%20to%20already%20contracted%20quantities.%20These%20apply%20to%20ethanol%20supply%20year%20(ESY)%202023-24%20(i.e.%2C%20November%202023%20to%20October%202024).%20Among%20other%20things%2C%20we%20deduce%20two%20things%20from%20this%3A%20(i)%20apart%20from%20grains%2C%20ethanol%20is%20mainly%20to%20come%20from%20the%20C-heavy%20molasses%20route%20in%20ESY%202023-24%2C%20and%20(ii)%20with%20smaller%20cane-based%20feedstock%2C%20ethanol%20blending%20performance%20this%20year%20is%20likely%20to%20fall%20below%20the%20levels%20of%20E12%20in%20ESY%202022-23.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20case%20of%20B-heavy%2C%20the%20government%20has%20permitted%20the%20quantities%20already%20contracted%20by%20oil%20companies%20to%20continue%20to%20be%20supplied.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202021-22%2C%202.36%20billion%20litres%20of%20B-heavy%20based%20ethanol%20was%20supplied%20to%20oil%20companies.%20In%202022-23%2C%20this%20fell%20to%202.27%20billion%20litres.%20In%202023-24%2C%20in%20light%20of%20a%20smaller%20sugarcane%20crop%2C%20quantities%20contracted%20by%20oil%20companies%20have%20fallen%20to%201.3%20billion%20litres.%20The%20government%20has%20pegged%20the%20annual%20supplies%20from%20B-heavy%20to%20this%20quantity%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECentrality%20of%20sugarcane%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20E20%20initiative%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20reduce%20country%E2%80%99s%20imported%20crude%20oil%20dependence%2C%20in%202018%20the%20government%20released%20its%20national%20policy%20on%20biofuels.%20Later%20in%202021%2C%20NITI%20Aayog%20followed%20it%20up%20with%20a%20roadmap%20for%20achieving%20targets%20under%20the%20policy.%20Through%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farcusresearch.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2FEthanol-blending-of-petrol-in-India-APR-.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eensuing%20journeys%20of%20the%20two%20documents%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20as%20it%20stands%20today%2C%20the%20country%20aims%20to%20achieve%2020%25%20blending%20in%20its%20fuel%20oil%20by%20year%202025-26.%20This%20target%20is%20referred%20to%20as%20E20%2C%20which%20implies%20that%20by%202025%2C%20a%20litre%20of%20fuel%20oil%20we%20would%20buy%20for%20our%20vehicles%20is%20likely%20to%20have%20200%20ml%20of%20ethanol%20and%20800%20ml%20of%20petroleum%20in%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fenergy%2Fwith-the-climate-crisis-on-e10-might-be-indias-ethanol-blending-sweet-spot%2F%5C%22%3EWith%20the%20Climate%20Crisis%20On%2C%20E10%20Might%20Be%20India%E2%80%99s%20Ethanol-Blending%20Sweet%20Spot%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.niti.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2021-06%2FEthanolBlendingInIndia_compressed.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENITI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Ayog%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20to%20achieve%20E20%2C%20country%20is%20likely%20to%20need%20about%2010.16%20billion%20litres%20of%20ethanol%20annually.%20It%20projected%20that%20close%20to%2050%25%20of%20this%20ethanol%20is%20to%20be%20produced%20from%20sugarcane%20derivatives%20and%20the%20remaining%20half%20is%20to%20come%20from%20grains%20like%20rice%20released%20by%20the%20Food%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(FCI)%2C%20broken%20rice%20from%20the%20open%20market%2C%20and%20maize.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20ESY%202022-23%2C%20the%20country%20achieved%20E12%20(12%25%20blending)%20which%20was%20the%20target%20for%20the%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20produced%20about%204.94%20billion%20litres%20of%20ethanol%20of%20which%20about%2075%25%20came%20from%20sugarcane-based%20sources%2C%2015%25%20from%20rice%20released%20by%20FCI%2C%204%25%20from%20maize%20and%20the%20remaining%205%25%20came%20from%20damaged%20food%20grains%2C%20including%20broken%20rice%20from%20open%20market.%20Within%20cane-based%20sources%2C%2063%25%20came%20from%20B-heavy%20molasses%20and%2035%25%20from%20juice.%20Sugarcane%20based%20ethanol%20production%20was%20projected%20to%20remain%20the%20mainstay%20of%20the%20ethanol%20production%20in%20the%20country.%20It%20was%20also%20envisaged%20that%20grain-based%20ethanol%20production%20would%20rise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EFigure%201%3A%20Contribution%20of%20cane-based%20feedstock%20in%20ESY%2022-23%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10200414%2Funnamed.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10200414%2Funnamed.png%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10200414%2Funnamed-293x300.png%20293w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688519%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20MOPNG.%20Data%20for%202022-23%20is%20till%20mid-October%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EWhy%20is%20there%20a%20panic%20on%20sugarcane%20crop%3F%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20sugarcane%20crop%20in%202023-24%20has%20suffered%20on%20account%20of%20volatile%20monsoon%20rains.%20Parts%20of%20Maharashtra%20and%20Karnataka%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Findia-working-prevent-disruption-ethanol-supplies-gasoline-blending-2023-12-08%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esuffered%20significant%20losses%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20cane%20yields%20and%20acreages.%20As%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fupag.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20government%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20sugarcane%20production%20in%202023-24%20is%20estimated%20at%20435%20million%20metric%20tonnes%20(MMTs)%20which%20is%20about%2056%20MMTs%20lower%20than%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20491%20MMTs.%20This%20implies%20that%20compared%20to%20last%20year%2C%20country%E2%80%99s%20sucrose%20production%20is%20likely%20to%20fall%20by%206%20MMTs%20(at%2011%25%20recovery%20rate).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20current%20year%2C%20opening%20stocks%20of%20sugar%20on%20October%201%2C%202023%20were%20about%205.7%20MMTs%20and%20with%20production%20shortfall%20of%206%20MMTs%2C%20the%20supply%20is%20likely%20to%20fall%20short%20of%20demand%20(about%2029%20MMTs)%20by%20about%202%20MMTs%20in%20the%20current%20year%2C%202023-24.%20Not%20surprisingly%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Fforeign-trade%2Findian-govt-extends-restriction-on-sugar-exports-beyond-oct-31%2Farticleshow%2F104517217.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20government%20banned%20sugar%20exports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20early%20in%20the%20year.%20By%20manoeuvring%20the%20ethanol%20production%20away%20from%20sugarcane-derivatives%2C%20the%20government%20has%20been%20able%20to%20reduce%20sucrose%20diversion%20to%20ethanol%20by%20about%202%20MMTs%20(calculated%20as%20back-of-envelope%20calculations).%20This%20may%20imply%20that%20the%20country%20could%20see%20through%20the%20next%20year%20with%20similar%20levels%20of%20inter-year%20stocks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20now%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20ESY%202023-24%2C%20the%20country%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.niti.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2021-06%2FEthanolBlendingInIndia_compressed.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaimed%20to%20achieve%20ethanol%20blending%20target%20of%20E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20appears%20inevitable%20that%20the%20performance%20will%20fall%20short%20of%20this%20target.%20With%20lower%20availability%20of%20molasses-based%20feedstock%2C%20and%20poorer%20availability%20of%20crops%20like%20rice%20and%20maize%2C%20maintaining%20current%20year%E2%80%99s%20E12%20also%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20challenge%20in%20ESY%202023-24.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20ethanol%20blending%20program%20is%20important%20in%20the%20larger%20scheme%20of%20things.%20While%20the%20country%20works%20to%20develop%20its%20crop%E2%80%99s%20resilience%20to%20droughts%20and%20pests%2C%20the%20need%20for%20improvement%20in%20crop%20yields%2C%20especially%20for%20maize%2C%20is%20absolutely%20urgent.%20The%20commercial%20production%20of%20second%20generation%20ethanol%20at%20viable%20rates%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20tested.%20If%20it%20is%20successful%20it%20can%20reduce%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fstubble-burning-problem-solutions-9033982%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estubble%20burning%20incidents%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShweta%20Saini%20is%20an%20agricultural%20economist%20and%20CEO%2C%20Arcus%20Policy%20Research%20and%20Siraj%20Hussain%20is%20former%20Union%20agriculture%20secretary%2C%20GOI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702219781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10201346%2Fsugarcane-farmer-in-a-queue-waiting-to-sell_Alamy_2HM25XN-1800x1201-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenergy%2Findia-is-likely-to-miss-its-ethanol-blending-target-this-year%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20per%20the%20NITI%20Ayog%2C%20to%20achieve%20E20%2C%20the%20country%20is%20likely%20to%20need%20about%2010.16%20billion%20litres%20of%20ethanol%20annually%20with%20sugarcane%20based%20ethanol%20as%20the%20mainstay%20of%20production.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenergy%2Findia-is-likely-to-miss-its-ethanol-blending-target-this-year%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Raman%20Singh%20New%20Chhattisgarh%20Speaker%2C%20Two%20Deputies%20For%20Vishnu%20Sai%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVishnu%20Deo%20Sai%2C%20the%20BJP's%20new%20tribal%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20will%20have%20two%20deputies%20--%20part%20of%20the%20party's%20efforts%20to%20balance%20the%20caste%20equation%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deputies%20are%20state%20BJP%20chief%20Arun%20Sao%20--%C2%A0%20a%20leader%20from%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20and%20Vijay%20Sharma%20--%20a%20Brahmin.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20also%20could%20not%20ignore%20Raman%20Singh%2C%20who%C2%A0%20has%20the%20experience%20of%20running%20the%20government%20for%2015%20years%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20BJP's%20campaign%20for%202024.%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20a%20Rajput%2C%20who%20was%20also%20a%20contender%20for%20the%20top%20post%20this%20time%2C%20will%20be%20the%20Assembly%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20Arun%20Sao%20was%20also%20in%20the%20running%20for%20the%20top%20job%20in%20the%20state%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20that%20the%20extra%20prominence%20will%20help%20keep%20factionalism%20at%20bay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20Sharma%20is%20a%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20party%20--%20and%20along%20with%20the%20new%20Chief%20Minister%20--%20also%20very%20close%20to%20Raman%20Singh.%20In%20the%20recently%20concluded%20assembly%20election%2C%20he%20defeated%20powerful%20minister%20Congress%20leader%20and%20state%20minister%20Mohamad%20Akbar%20from%20Kawardha%C2%A0%20constituency%20by%20around%2040%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20team%20selection%20for%20Chhattisgarh%20was%20made%20after%20a%20week%20of%20deliberations%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20idea%20of%20having%20a%20tribal%20leader%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20tribal-dominated%20state.%20The%20BJP%20has%20won%20all%2014%20assembly%20seats%20in%20the%20tribal-dominated%20Surguja%20region%20and%20eight%20of%20the%2012%20seats%20in%20Bastar%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20representation%20of%20OBCs%20--%20the%20other%20huge%20chunk%20of%20the%20state's%20population%20--%20an%20OBC%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20named%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20claims%20that%20Mr%20Sai%20is%20the%20first%20tribal%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20always%20contradicted%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Jogi's%20status%20as%20a%20tribal.%20His%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%20was%20challenged%20in%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20high%20court%2C%20which%20ordered%20that%20a%20committee%20be%20set%20up%20to%20examine%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20a%20case%20was%20filed%20against%20him%20after%20his%20tribal%20status%20claim%20was%20rejected%20by%20a%20government-appointed%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702218660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fceffi72c_arun-sao-vijay-sharma-_625x300_10_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farun-sao-and-vijay-sharma-to-be-chhattisgarh-deputy-chief-ministers-raman-singh-will-be-speaker-say-sources-4651384%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arun%20Sao%20and%20Vijay%20Sharma%20to%20be%20Chhattisgarh%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%3B%20Raman%20Singh%20will%20be%20Speaker%2C%20say%20sources%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2