0CEO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20ChatGPT%20maker%20OpenAI%20witnessed%20a%20harrowing%20time%20after%20it%20fired%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman.%20The%20artificial%20intelligence%20community%20witnessed%20high%20drama%20for%20five%20days%20before%20OpenAI%20reached%20an%20agreement%20to%20bring%20back%20Sam%20Altman%20as%20the%20CEO%20and%20appoint%20new%20board%20members%20after%20nearly%20all%20of%20its%20employees%20threatened%20to%20quit%20over%20his%20ouster.%20The%20company's%20President%20and%20co-founder%20Greg%20Brockman%20also%20rejoined%20after%20a%20chaotic%20period%20that%20highlighted%20deep%20tensions%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20community.%20Now%2C%20speaking%20to%20Trevor%20Noah%20on%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Fshow%2F122imavATqSE7eCyXIcqZL%23login%5C%22%3EWhat%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20podcast%2C%20Mr%20Altman%20stated%20that%20he%20learnt%20a%20lot%20from%20the%20whole%20incident%20despite%20its%20%26quot%3Bpainful%20cost%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20empathy%20I%20gained%20out%20of%20this%20whole%20experience%2C%20and%20my%20recompilation%20of%20values%2C%20for%20sure%20was%20a%20blessing%20in%20disguise.%20It%20was%20at%20a%20painful%20cost%2C%20but%20I'm%20happy%20to%20have%20had%20the%20experience%20in%20that%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Altman%20was%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20for%20the%20Formula%20One%20Grand%20Prix%20when%20he%20got%20the%20news%20that%20the%20board%20had%20sacked%20him.%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20got%20to%20watch%20any%20race%20that%20whole%20weekend.%20I%20was%20in%20my%20hotel%20room%2C%20took%20this%20call%2C%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20it%20was%20gonna%20be%2C%20and%20got%20fired%20by%20the%20board.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mr%20Altman%2C%20his%20phone%20began%20to%20overflow%20with%20texts%20to%20the%20point%20that%20iMessage%20stopped%20functioning.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20in%20the%20next%20like%20half%20hour%2C%20I%20got%20so%20many%20messages%20that%20iMessage%20like%20broke%20on%20my%20phone.%20My%20phone%20was%20just%20unusable%20because%20it%20was%20just%20like%20notifications%20non-stop%20and%20iMessage%20like%20hit%20this%20thing%20where%20it%20stopped%20working%20for%20a%20while.%20That%20message%20got%20delivered%20late%2C%20then%20it%20marked%20everything%20as%20read%2C%20so%20I%20couldn't%20even%20like%20tell%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20he%20stated%20he%20was%20not%20considering%20going%20back%20to%20OpenAI%20just%20yet%2C%20he%20was%20certain%20he%20wanted%20to%20continue%20working%20on%20creating%20generalised%20artificial%20intelligence.%20%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20like%20a%20dream.%20I%20was%20confused%2C%20it%20was%20chaotic.%20It%20did%20not%20feel%20real%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20saga%20is%20over%2C%20the%20CEO%20still%20has%20some%20hard%20feelings%20about%20the%20whole%20ordeal.%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20very%20painful%20thing%20and%20felt%20to%20me%2C%20personally%2C%20just%20as%20a%20human%2C%20super%20unfair%20-%20the%20way%20it%20was%20handled%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Mr%20Altman%20was%20also%20named%20the%20%26quot%3BCEO%20of%20the%20year%26quot%3B%20by%20Time%20Magazine%20for%20his%20remarkable%20contributions%20to%20the%20tech%20industry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702217520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fhptnt2j_sam-altman_625x300_22_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fblessing-in-disguise-sam-altman-reflects-on-being-fired-as-openai-ceo-4651540%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mr%20Altman%20was%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20for%20the%20Formula%20One%20Grand%20Prix%20when%20he%20got%20the%20news%20that%20the%20board%20had%20sacked%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%