business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F05%2Ffull%2F1680674554-5502.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-projects-to-raise-up-to-rs-750-cr-via-non-convertible-debentures-123121000655_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TPL%20raised%20two%20subordinated%20NCDs%20of%20Rs%20500%20crore%20each%20in%20FY22%20and%20FY23%2C%20which%20have%20a%20redemption%20tenure%20of%20six%20and%20half%20years%20and%20six%20years%2C%20respectively%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-projects-to-raise-up-to-rs-750-cr-via-non-convertible-debentures-123121000655_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gupkar%20Parties%20vs%20BJP%20Ahead%20Of%20Supreme%20Court's%20Article%20370%20Verdict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20pronounce%20its%20verdict%20on%20Monday%20on%20the%20constitutional%20validity%20of%20the%20Centre's%20decision%20to%20abrogate%20controversial%20Article%20370%2C%20several%20parties%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20expressed%20hope%20that%20the%20provision%20will%20be%20restored%2C%20while%20on%20the%20ground%20authorities%20have%20made%20%26quot%3Badequate%26quot%3B%20security%20arrangements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20said%20that%20there%20should%20not%20be%20any%20politics%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20and%20everyone%20should%20respect%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20Conference%20leader%20Omar%20Abdullah%20said%20his%20party%20will%20not%20disturb%20the%20peace%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20even%20in%20case%20of%20an%20adverse%20verdict%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20the%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20will%20continue%20its%20fight%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople's%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%20president%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20said%20the%20court's%20verdict%20should%20be%20clear%20that%20the%20decision%20taken%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20was%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NC%20and%20PDP%20are%20part%20of%20the%20People's%20Alliance%20for%20Gupkar%20Declaration%20(PAGD)%2C%20also%20called%20the%20Gupkar%20Alliance%2C%20which%20was%20formed%20by%20parties%20in%C2%A0J%26amp%3BK%C2%A0%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20chief%20minister%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20expressed%20hope%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20deliver%20a%20verdict%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20slew%20of%20restrictions%20was%20placed%20in%C2%A0J%26amp%3BK%C2%A0%20and%20scores%20of%20leaders%20were%20detained%20or%20put%20under%20house%20arrest%20when%20Article%20370%20which%20gave%20special%20status%20to%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20scrapped%20and%20J-K%20was%20bifurcated%20into%20Union%20territories%20on%20August%205%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20apprehensions%20expressed%20by%20many%20parties%20about%20the%20aftermath%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20stressed%20that%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20drop%20of%20blood%20was%20shed%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20critical%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScrapping%20Article%20370%20was%20among%20the%20core%20issues%20of%20BJP's%20agenda%20and%20had%20been%20consistently%20included%20in%20its%20election%20manifestos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmar%20Abdullah%20on%20Sunday%20said%20his%20party%20will%20continue%20its%20fight%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20rights%20of%20people%20through%20peaceful%20means%20as%20laid%20down%20in%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20to%20give%20its%20verdict%2C%20let%20it.%20If%20we%20had%20to%20disturb%20the%20situation%2C%20we%20would%20have%20done%20it%20after%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20we%20said%20it%20then%20and%20we%20reiterate%20it%20now%20that%20our%20fight%20will%20be%20peaceful%20and%20as%20per%20the%20Constitution%2C%20taking%20the%20help%20of%20the%20law%20to%20protect%20our%20rights%20and%20preserve%20our%20identity.%20What%20is%20wrong%20with%20it%3F%20Don't%20we%20have%20a%20right%20to%20say%20this%20in%20a%20democracy%3F%20Can't%20we%20raise%20objections%20in%20a%20democracy%3F%20If%20others%20can%20talk%2C%20why%20not%20us%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20party%20convention%20at%20Rafiabad%20in%20Baramulla%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%20claimed%20that%20police%20had%20been%20summoning%20National%20Conference%20leaders%20to%20police%20stations%20since%20Saturday%20night%20and%20%26quot%3Bintimidating%26quot%3B%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20not%20passed%20a%20verdict%20yet.%20How%20do%20you%20know%20what%20is%20the%20verdict%3F%20Maybe%20it%20is%20in%20our%20favour!%20Then%20what%20is%20the%20need%20to%20call%20my%20party%20colleagues%20to%20police%20stations...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAllah%20willing%2C%20if%20the%20verdict%20goes%20against%20them%20(BJP)%2C%20what%20will%20you%20do%20if%20they%20start%20writing%20against%20it%20on%20Facebook%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%20said%20there%20was%20no%20justification%20to%20put%20curbs%20on%20National%20Conference%20leaders%20as%20they%20have%20always%20been%20votaries%20of%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20knocked%20at%20the%20door%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20getting%20justice%20and%20that%20sentiment%20persists%20even%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Azad%20said%20only%20two%20institutions%20that%20can%20return%20articles%20370%20and%2035A%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20-%20Parliament%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20is%20non-partisan%20and%20we%20hope%20that%20it%20will%20give%20a%20decision%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Azad%2C%20who%20floated%20the%20Democratic%20Progressive%20Azad%20Party%20(DPAP)%20after%20parting%20ways%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20said%20he%20cannot%20foresee%20Parliament%20reversing%20the%20decisions%20taken%20on%20August%205%2C%202019%2C%20as%20it%20would%20require%20a%20two-thirds%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Azad%20said%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20religion%20or%20ethnicity%2C%20have%20an%20emotional%20attachment%20to%20the%20special%20provisions%20of%20the%20Constitution%20that%20were%20repealed%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20that%20these%20(provisions)%20are%20restored%20for%20securing%20our%20present%20and%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP's%20J%26amp%3BK%C2%A0unit%20chief%20Ravinder%20Raina%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20heard%20both%20sides%20through%20a%20transparent%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20confident%20that%20it%20will%20no%20longer%20remain%20a%20political%20issue%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict.%20We%20are%20all%20citizens%20of%20this%20democratic%20country%20and%20everyone%20should%20respect%20and%20accept%20whatever%20decision%20the%20honourable%20Supreme%20Court%20takes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20judiciary%20is%20the%20greatest.%20There%20should%20be%20no%20politics%20on%20the%20verdict%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Raina%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehbooba%20Mufti%20said%20it%20is%20the%20top%20court's%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20does%20not%20push%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20(BJP)%20agenda%2C%20but%20keeps%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20country%20and%20its%20Constitution%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20decision%20should%20be%20simple%20that%20whatever%20was%20done%20on%20August%205%2C%202019%2C%20was%20illegal%2C%20unconstitutional%2C%20against%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20the%20promises%20made%20to%20the%20people%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20authorities%20said%20they%20have%20made%20adequate%20security%20arrangements%20to%20ensure%20that%20peace%20is%20not%20disturbed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20duty-bound%20to%20ensure%20that%20peace%20prevails%20in%20the%20Valley%20under%20all%20circumstances%2C%26quot%3B%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Police%20(IGP)%2C%20Kashmir%20Zone%20V%20K%20Birdi%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20IGP%20refused%20to%20divulge%20specifics%20of%20the%20security%20set-up%20for%20Monday%2C%20he%20said%20%26quot%3Badequate%20arrangements%26quot%3B%20have%20been%20put%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20taking%20all%20precautions%20and%20will%20ensure%20that%20peace%20is%20not%20disturbed%20in%20Kashmir%2C%26quot%3B%20Birdi%2C%20who%20held%20security%20review%20meetings%20in%20most%20of%20the%2010%20valley%20districts%20over%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20orders%20invoking%20section%20144%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CrPC)%20on%20the%20misuse%20of%20social%20media%20were%20related%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20expected%20judgment%2C%20he%20said%20there%20have%20been%20several%20incidents%20of%20some%20elements%20trying%20to%20provoke%20people%20with%20their%20posts.%20%26quot%3BAction%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20such%20elements%20in%20the%20past%20and%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20in%20the%20future%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20here%20have%20issued%20guidelines%20for%20social%20media%20users%20under%20CrPC%20section%20144%20to%20curb%20the%20spread%20of%20any%20content%20that%20is%20communally%20sensitive%20or%20promotes%20terrorism%20and%20secessionism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20guidelines%20aim%20to%20provide%20clarity%20on%20actions%20citizens%20should%20take%20when%20encountering%20content%20related%20to%20terrorism%2C%20secessionism%2C%20threats%2C%20intimidation%20or%20communally-sensitive%20material%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20circular%2C%20issued%20by%20police%20in%20several%20districts%2C%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20top%20court%20reserved%20its%20verdict%20on%20the%20petitions%20on%20September%205%20after%20conducting%20daily%20hearings%20on%20the%20matter%20from%20August%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20cause%20list%20for%20December%2011%20(Monday)%2C%20uploaded%20on%20the%20top%20court's%20website%2C%20a%20five-judge%20Constitution%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20D%20Y%20Chandrachud%20would%20deliver%20the%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20members%20of%20the%20bench%20are%20Justices%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul%2C%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20B%20R%20Gavai%2C%20and%20Surya%20Kant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20petition%20challenging%20the%20presidential%20order%20scrapping%20Article%20370%20was%20filed%20by%20advocate%20M%20L%20Sharma%2C%20who%20was%20later%20joined%20by%20another%20lawyer%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Shakir%20Shabir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20Conference%20filed%20a%20petition%20on%20August%2010.%20The%20petition%20was%20filed%20by%20Mohammad%20Akbar%20Lone%20and%20Justice%20(retd)%20Hasnain%20Masoodi%2C%20both%20Lok%20Sabha%20members%20of%20the%20NC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20Centre's%20decision%20to%20abrogate%20Article%20370%2C%20including%20a%20plea%20filed%20by%20a%20group%20of%20former%20defence%20officers%20and%20bureaucrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20s