plaint%20details%20the%20assault%2C%20threats%2C%20and%20allegations%20over%20the%20illegal%20encroachment%20of%20Surajmal%20Regar%E2%80%99s%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20related%20matter%2C%20a%20complaint%20has%20also%20been%20lodged%20with%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20against%20Balmukund%20Acharya%20for%20violating%20street%20vendor%20laws.%20This%20incident%20occurred%20when%20the%20MLA%20visited%20the%20Hawa%20Mahal%20area%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Frajasthan-bjp-mla-who-shut-down-meat-shops-a-day-after-election-win-apologises%5C%22%3Einstructed%3C%2Fa%3E%20Muslim%20vendors%20to%20close%20their%20shops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20FIR%20encompasses%20charges%20under%20IPC%20Sections%20341%20(wrongful%20restraint)%20and%20323%20(voluntarily%20causing%20hurt)%2C%20along%20with%20SC%2FST%20Act%20provisions.%20These%20provisions%20include%203(1)r%20SC%2FST%20(intentionally%20insulting%20or%20intimidating%20a%20member%20of%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20or%20Tribe%20and%20abusing%20them%20by%20caste%20name%20in%20public%20view)%3B%203(1)(s)%20(abusing%20any%20member%20of%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20or%20a%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20by%20caste%20name%20in%20any%20place%20within%20public%20view)%3B%20and%203(2)%20va%20(committing%20any%20offence%20specified%20in%20the%20Schedule%20against%20a%20person%20or%20property%2C%20knowing%20that%20such%20person%20is%20a%20member%20of%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20or%20a%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20or%20such%20property%20belongs%20to%20such%20a%20member%2C%20shall%20be%20punishable%20with%20such%20punishment%20as%20specified%20under%20the%20IPC%20for%20such%20offenses%20and%20shall%20also%20be%20liable%20to%20a%20fine.)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702211417000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06103243%2FScreenshot-2023-12-06-at-10.30.47-AM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Frajasthan-fir-against-ha