ml%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbimal-dayal-appointed-as-ceo-of-adani-infra-will-oversee-energy-projects-123120900318_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Backstory%3A%20Polls%2C%20Verdicts%20and%20Media%20Narratives%20on%20Counting%20Day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F03190918%2FScreenshot-2022-02-03-at-7.09.01-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENothing%20perhaps%20shines%20the%20light%20on%20the%20nexus%20between%20media%20power%2C%20money%20power%20and%20political%20power%20better%20than%20the%20narrative%20generated%20by%20Big%20Media%20on%20counting%20day.%20The%20effort%20as%20always%20is%20to%20make%20these%20shows%2C%20fuelled%20by%20an%20endless%20river%20of%20ads%2C%20as%20entertaining%20as%20possible%20with%20its%20colourful%20cast%20of%20characters%20and%20its%20edge-of-the-seat%2C%20nail-biting%20suspense.%20Sophisticated%20data%20crunching%20and%20display%20keep%20stoking%20audience%20curiosity%20through%20a%20template%20that%20recalls%20the%20money-spinning%20show%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKaun%20Banega%20Crorepati%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(Who%20Wants%20To%20Be%20a%20Millionaire).%20Larger-than-life%20figures%20are%20made%20to%20loom%20even%20larger%3B%20even%20as%20those%20poor%20sods%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20the%20cut%20are%20stomped%20into%20the%20dust.%20The%20presumption%20is%20that%20the%20show%20that%20can%20suss%20out%20the%20winning%20candidates%20before%20they%20have%20actually%20won%20helped%20perhaps%20by%20other%20money%20spinners%20like%20exit%20polls%3B%20the%20show%20that%20provides%20the%20tallies%20at%20the%20fastest%20pace%2C%20is%20somehow%20the%20most%20credible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWriting%20on%20the%20recent%20elections%20in%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20Katjana%20Gattermann%2C%20who%20studies%20how%20the%20media%20influences%20elections%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uva.nl%2Fen%2Fshared-content%2Ffaculteiten%2Fen%2Ffaculteit-der-maatschappij-en-gedragswetenschappen%2Fnews%2F2023%2F11%2Fthe-influence-of-media-framing-of-election-results.html%5C%22%3Eargued%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20mainstream%20media%20%E2%80%9Cthrough%20their%20coverage%2C%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20legitimising%20elections%20and%20fostering%20acceptance%20of%20the%20results%2C%20as%20well%20as%20framing%20winners%20and%20losers.%E2%80%9D%20The%20picture%20is%20not%20too%20different%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Indian%20elections%20as%20we%20saw%20on%20December%203%20%E2%80%93%20Counting%20Day.%C2%A0%20In%20many%20ways%2C%20these%20programmes%20with%20their%20formulaic%20devices%20and%20expert%20commentary%20crucially%20influence%20Indian%20electoral%20democracy.%20Their%20impacts%20live%20on%20long%20after%20the%20show%20itself%20comes%20to%20an%20end%2C%20influencing%20how%20politics%20plays%20out%20in%20metropolitan%20centres%20and%20mofussil%20%3Cem%3Enukkads%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20how%20ordinary%20citizens%20come%20to%20assess%20their%20leaders%20and%20make%20voting%20decisions%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProgrammes%20like%20these%20may%20of%20course%20have%20played%20a%20positive%20role%20by%20helping%20raise%20political%20awareness%20at%20a%20more%20general%20level.%20But%2C%20equally%2C%20they%20foster%20a%20sense%20that%20one%20leader%20is%20prime%20and%20one%20party%20is%20unbeatable%2C%20and%20that%20perhaps%20there%20is%20no%20option%20but%20to%20vote%20them%20in.%20Such%20consequences%20could%20be%20severely%20debilitating%20to%20the%20election%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIs%20it%20then%20possible%20to%20imagine%20another%20way%20to%20conduct%20Counting%20Day%20conversations%20on%20public%20media%3F%20Perhaps%2C%20if%20we%20are%20to%20go%20by%20the%20recent%20effort%20of%20five%20independent%20news%20organisations%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Caravan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewslaundry%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EScroll.in%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20this%20news%20portal%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20coming%20together%20on%20Counting%20Day%20to%20tell%20their%20audiences%20the%20story%20of%20these%20elections%20to%20the%20state%20assemblies%20of%20Mizoram%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Telangana%2C%20and%20to%20breakdown%20the%20verdicts.%20This%20is%20the%20second%20time%20this%20cohort%20has%20conducted%20such%20an%20experiment%20%E2%80%93%20the%20first%20being%20in%20May%2C%20when%20the%20Karnataka%20poll%20results%20came%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20saw%20counting%20day%20as%20a%20moment%20they%20needed%20to%20seize%20because%20it%20was%20also%20a%20moment%20when%20%E2%80%9Ccitizens%20of%20a%20free%20country%20speak%20truth%20to%20those%20in%20power%E2%80%9D.%20Many%20would%20question%20whether%20citizens%2C%20by%20their%20act%20of%20voting%2C%20do%20indeed%20speak%20truth%20to%20power%2C%20or%20whether%20they%20are%20more%20influenced%20by%20what%20the%20prime%20minister%20had%20once%20colourfully%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Erevdi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(a%20sweet%20form%20of%20a%20freebie)%2C%20until%20of%20course%20his%20own%20party%20outdid%20the%20rest%20in%20such%20distribution.%20Many%20more%20will%20question%20whether%20the%20country%20is%20still%20free.%20But%20let%20us%20put%20such%20cavils%20aside%20and%20examine%20what%20was%20on%20offer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20striking%20feature%20of%20this%20conversation%20was%20that%20it%20was%20truly%20a%20conversation%20%E2%80%93%20with%20speakers%20being%20allowed%20to%20formulate%20their%20thoughts%20in%20a%20fairly%20leisurely%20fashion.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20a%20dazzling%20insight%20may%20emerge%20that%20rarely%20makes%20its%20way%20into%20such%20settings.%20Has%20competitive%20welfarism%20emerged%20as%20the%20main%20driver%20of%20elections%20in%20India%20today%3F%20Could%20the%20cash%20benefit%20transfers%2C%20the%20new%20face%20of%20state%20welfarism%20in%20India%2C%20be%20considered%20as%20part%20of%20Liberalisation%200.2%2C%20with%20the%20state%20ceding%20space%20to%20make%20policy%20decisions%20for%20popular%20well-being%20to%20the%20market%3F%20Do%20these%20%E2%80%9Ccash%20transfer%20regimes%E2%80%9D%20help%20or%20hinder%20aspects%20like%20education%2C%20when%20for%20instance%20money%20that%20had%20been%20earmarked%20for%20schooling%20and%20sent%20to%20beneficiaries%20end%20up%20being%20spent%20on%20consumables%3F%20Does%20such%20a%20model%20bypass%20local%20structures%20of%20delivery%20and%20create%20an%20emotional%20connect%20between%20the%20voter%20and%20the%20figure%20who%20is%20seen%20as%20responsible%20for%20the%20largesse%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20the%20prime%20minister%20or%20a%20powerful%20chief%20minister%3F%20Does%20excessive%20reliance%20on%20ruling%20parties%20distributing%20tangible%20freebies%20to%20voters%20result%20in%20state%20exchequers%20being%20emptied%2C%20resulting%20in%20spending%20on%20the%20old%20tangibles%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebijli%2C%20sadak%2C%20pani%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20being%20severely%20curtailed%3F%20Are%20these%20freebies%20emerging%20as%20compensation%20for%20labour%20markets%20failing%20to%20employ%20workers%20in%20the%20way%20they%20want%20to%20be%20employed%3F%20Extremely%20crucial%20unpacking%20that%20has%20never%20figured%20sufficiently%20in%20the%20Big%20Media%E2%80%99s%20counting%20day%20coverage%2C%20denying%20citizens%20of%20an%20understanding%20that%20even%20as%20they%20welcome%20free%20grain%20or%20money%20coming%20into%20their%20bank%20accounts%2C%20it%20is%20they%20who%20end%20up%20paying%20a%20huge%20cost%20in%20terms%20of%20infrastructure%20and%20meaningful%20employment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20were%20conversations%20free%20of%20being%20straitjacketed%20by%20considerations%20of%20offending%20a%20particular%20advertiser%20or%20party%20patron%20and%20the%20critique%20often%20cuts%20deep.%20The%20anxiety%20to%20wear%20Hindutva%20on%20their%20sleeve%20by%20Congress%20figures%20like%20Bupesh%20Baghel%20through%20Ramayan%20festivals%20or%20Kamal%20Nath%20through%20Hanuman%20statues%20(but%20to%20such%20little%20effect)%2C%20was%20called%20out%20time%20and%20again%2C%20as%20indeed%20the%20drive%20of%20an%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20to%20emerge%20as%20sole%20icon%20and%20provider%20for%20the%20people%20of%20his%20state%20in%20a%20Modi-like%20manner.%20The%20overwhelming%20consensus%20was%20that%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20messaging%20has%20failed%20to%20keep%20Hindutva%20at%20bay%2C%20in%20fact%20to%20the%20contrary.%20The%20party%20leadership%20has%20also%20failed%20abysmally%20in%20keeping%20factional%20strife%20in%20check%2C%20and%20ended%20up%20paying%20a%20huge%20price.%20While%20the%20Pilot-Gehlot%20tussle%20led%20to%20a%20severe%20loss%20of%20votes%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20Gujjar%20region%2C%20the%20one%20between%20Baghel-T.S.%20Singhdeo%20(the%20latter%20was%20panchayat%20minister)%20ensured%20that%20the%20empowering%20impacts%20of%20Panchayat%20Extension%20of%20Schedule%20Area%20Act%20could%20not%20adequately%20reach%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29081646%2FGABI58kWMAANlJC.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29081646%2FGABI58kWMAANlJC.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29081646%2FGABI58kWMAANlJC-300x148.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29081646%2FGABI58kWMAANlJC-1024x506.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686839%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22593%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20leaders%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20campaigning%20in%20Telangana.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40INC4India%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fear%20of%20the%20Modi%20machinery%20often%20ensures%20that%20no%20criticism%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20is%20countenanced%20in%20the%20Big%20Media%20conversations%2C%20with%20self-censorship%20very%20much%20in%20play%20and%20even%20those%20invited%20as%20experts%20being%20briefed%20to%20avoid%20naming%20individuals.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20such%20restraint%20may%20have%20been%20there%20but%20it%20was%20not%20obvious.%20There%20was%20discussion%20on%20the%20cult-building%20exercises%20around%20the%20Modi%20figure.%20When%20asked%20how%20was%20it%20that%20many%20voters%20believed%20that%20India%20gave%20China%20a%20bloody%20nose%2C%20one%20of%20the%20speakers%20responded%20simply%3A%20%E2%80%9CWell%2C%20propaganda%20works.%E2%80%9D%20Clearly%2C%20the%20cult-building%20of%20Modi%20in%20the%20decade%20of%20his%20rule%20has%20not%20diminished%20in%20the%20least%20and%20the%20constant%20effort%20is%20to%20centralise%20elections%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20Modi%20could%20have%20a%20decisive%20impact.%20The%20double%20part%20of%20the%20engine%20becomes%20irrelevant%20since%20the%20single-engine%20works%20so%20spectacularly.%20Everywhere%20in%20the%20Hindi%20belt%2C%20the%20perception%20has%20grown%2C%20although%20these%20were%20state%20elections%2C%20that%20it%20was%20this%20one%20man%20who%20is%20the%20chief%20provider%20and%20creator.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInteresting%20discussions%20centred%20on%20the%20figure%20of%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20who%20perhaps%20of%20all%20the%20BJP%20chief%20ministers%20in%20India%20today%20had%20proved%20that%20he%20could%20deliver%20results%20despite%20not%20having%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20unqualified%20approval.%20Not%20only%20did%20he%20jettison%20the%20%E2%80%98Bulldozer%20Mama%E2%80%99%20image%20he%20tried%20to%20cultivate%20at%20one%20point%2C%20he%20projected%20himself%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccaring%20loving%20uncle%E2%80%9D%20and%20mounted%20a%20bruising%20campaign.%20This%20and%20his%20direct%20conversations%20with%20the%20electorate%2C%20especially%20with%20women%20voters%2C%20ensuring%20a%20verdict%20that%20defied%20the%20anti-incumbency%20of%20three%20terms.%20Interestingly%2C%20he%20has%20also%20beaten%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20record%20in%20terms%20of%20chief%20ministership%20and%20can%20even%20perhaps%20achieve%20the%20unthinkable%20and%20lay%20claim%20to%20becoming%20a%20future%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20it%20would%20be%20unthinkable%20to%20have%20the%20Big%20Media%20recognise%20the%20damage%20that%20surveillance%20and%20unremitting%20policing%20had%20done%20to%20TRS%2FBRS%20prospects%20in%20Telangana.%20Ten%20lakh%20CCTV%20cameras%20and%20police%20sweeping%20the%20state%20free%20of%20protests%20may%20not%20have%20been%20a%20major%20talking%20point%20but%20they%20did%20raise%20resentment%20in%20the%20ranks%20of%20the%20public%20and%20civil%20society.%20Or%20take%20the%20fact%20that%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20much%20acclaimed%20Rythu%20Bandhu%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Escheme%20had%20benefitted%20landed%20farmers%20ignoring%20the%20reality%20that%20most%20cultivators%20don%E2%80%99t%20own%20land.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20there%20were%20discussions%20on%20the%20OBC%20factor%2C%20the%20women%20voters%2C%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20social%20engineering%2C%20these%20topics%20also%20figured%20in%20Big%20Media%20coverage.%20However%2C%20not%20many%20in%20the%20mainstream%20bothered%20to%20dwell%20too%20deeply%20on%20the%20Muslim%20voter%2C%20and%20if%20they%20did%2C%20the%20label%20of%20%E2%80%9Cappeasement%20politics%E2%80%9D%20was%20never%20far%20away.%20It%20is%20in%20this%20context%20that%20the%20much-reviled%20figure%20of%20Asaduddin%20Salahuddin%20Owaisi%2C%20constantly%20framed%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cspoiler%E2%80%9D%2C%20needed%20to%20be%20reconsidered.%20One%20set%20of%20discussions%20in%20the%20independent%20media%20coverage%20recognised%20that%20he%20had%20single-handedly%20raised%20the%20value%20of%20the%20Muslim%20voter.%20The%20tropes%20he%20dwelt%20on%20may%20not%20be%20appetising%20for%20Hindutva-saturated%20television%20audiences%2C%20but%20it%20was%20an%20articulation%20that%20must%20exist%20given%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20reluctance%20to%20take%20Muslim%20repression%20head-on.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETowards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20eight-hour%20programme%2C%20when%20it%20had%20become%20clear%20that%20the%20Congress%20now%20had%20only%20a%20tenuous%20hold%20on%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%2C%20the%20question%20arose%20about%20what%20can%20be%20done.%20The%20counter-intuitive%20consensus%20was%20that%20a%20chastened%20Congress%20may%20be%20better%20for%20the%20survival%20of%20the%20INDIA%20block%2C%20with%20each%20individual%20party%20in%20the%20state%20where%20it%20is%20the%20strongest%20be%20allowed%20to%20set%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20electoral%20vision%20for%20that%20state.%20Finally%2C%20it%20is%20all%20about%20the%20kind%20of%20alternative%20vision%20that%20this%20conglomerate%20can%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20there%20was%20much%20to%20be%20said%20for%20this%20effort%2C%20there%20is%20a%20formidable%20list%20of%20misses%20too.%20They%20range%20from%20the%20simple%20%E2%80%93%20clearly%20labelling%20speakers%20while%20they%20are%20on%20the%20screen%20%E2%80%93%20to%20the%20more%20complicated%20job%20of%20deepening%20language%20connect%20with%20audiences.%20The%20scale%20of%20dubbing%20that%20the%20UN%20adopts%20is%20clearly%20unaffordable%20for%20a%20modest%20initiative%20like%20this%2C%20but%20at%20least%20Hindi-English%20translations%20of%20key%20points%20could%20be%20projected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20rizzy%20reportage%20from%20the%20ground%20(even%20Mizoram%2C%20where%20counting%20had%20been%20postponed%20to%20the%20following%20day%20received%20a%20little%20space)%20which%20inter-spliced%20the%20commentary%2C%20but%20there%20is%20scope%20for%20making%20these%20reports%20more%20succinct.%20On%20the%20whole%2C%20though%2C%20this%20is%20an%20effort%20that%20needs%20both%20financial%20and%20viewer%20support%20as%20we%20head%20for%20another%20general%20election.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20signing%20off%20line%20by%20one%20of%20the%20anchors%20was%20rife%20with%20possibilities%3A%20%E2%80%9CSee%20you%20next%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02220805%2FEffect-10.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02220805%2FEffect-10.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02220805%2FEffect-10-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02220805%2FEffect-10-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687426%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAgencies%20seizing%20journalists%E2%80%99%20devices%3A%20Why%20is%20the%20govt%20dragging%20its%20feet%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20every%20journalist%2C%20scholar%2C%20civil%20activist%20who%20has%20come%20under%20the%20scrutiny%20of%20the%20security%20agencies%20of%20the%20government%2C%20here%20are%20some%20questions%20of%20grave%20urgency%3A%20Why%20are%20electronic%20devices%20crucial%20for%20professional%20functioning%20seized%20by%20security%20agencies%20without%20proper%20warrants%3F%20How%20can%20these%20agencies%2C%20once%20they%20have%20seized%20these%20devices%2C%20retain%20them%20for%20interminable%20lengths%20of%20time%3F%20Why%20cannot%20agencies%20make%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20content%20that%20they%20consider%20material%20to%20their%20case%2C%20rather%20than%20impound%20all%20the%20material%2C%20personal%2C%20and%20privileged%2C%20in%20a%20confiscated%20device%3F%20These%20are%20only%20some%20of%20the%20questions%20that%20have%20arisen%20over%20the%20impunity%20with%20which%20devices%20have%20been%20seized%20during%20raids%20conducted%20over%20several%20years%20%E2%80%93%20most%20recently%20when%20some%20300%20devices%20of%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fweeks-after-unprecedented-raids-newsclick-staffers-grapple-with-waiting-game%5C%22%3E50%20journalists%20were%20confiscated%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20during%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20raids.%20Deeply%20troubling%20as%20these%20questions%20are%2C%20the%20government%20is%20in%20no%20hurry%20to%20answer%20them%2C%20and%20the%20agencies%20are%20in%20no%20hurry%20to%20return%20the%20devices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20two-member%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20now%20deciding%20three%20connected%20petitions%20%E2%80%93%20the%20first%20filed%20by%20academics%20Ram%20Ramaswamy%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eet%20al%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20in%202021%20and%20two%20others%2C%20the%20Foundation%20for%20Media%20Professionals%20and%20Amazon%20Seller%20Services%20Private%20Limited%20respectively%20%E2%80%93%20seeking%20unambiguous%20guidelines%20over%20the%20seizure%20of%20devices%20during%20such%20search-and-seizure%20raids.%20At%20a%20sitting%20last%20month%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20had%20observed%20that%20these%20guidelines%20are%20vital%20and%20that%20unchecked%2C%20%E2%80%9Call-pervading%E2%80%9D%20power%20with%20investigating%20agencies%20is%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20very%20dangerous%E2%80%9D.%20One%20of%20the%20judges%20roundly%20told%20the%20government%20through%20its%20additional%20solicitor%20general%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20must%20have%20some%20guidelines.%20You%20want%20us%20to%20do%20it%2C%20we%20will%20do%20it.%20But%20my%20view%20is%20that%20you%20ought%20to%20do%20it%20yourself.%E2%80%9D%20A%20month%20has%20passed%20since%20those%20observations%20were%20made%2C%20but%20the%20additional%20solicitor%20general%20returned%20to%20the%20court%20last%20week%2C%20empty-handed%2C%20asking%20for%20a%20week%20more%20to%20submit%20the%20guidelines.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGoing%20by%20the%20arguments%20the%20government%20has%20made%20before%20the%20court%20thus%20far%2C%20and%20its%20repressive%20instincts%2C%20there%20is%20no%20guarantee%20that%20it%20will%20indeed%20come%20up%20with%20such%20guidelines%20in%20the%20stipulated%20time.%20%E2%80%9CLegitimate%20state%20interests%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20its%20thinking%2C%20trumps%20privacy%20rights.%20Bureaucratese%20worthy%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FHumphrey_Appleby%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESir%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHumphrey%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FHumphrey_Appleby%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Appleby%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0marked%20its%20affidavit%3A%20It%20argued%20that%20a%20blanket%20order%20regarding%20the%20return%20of%20digital%20devices%20to%20persons%20under%20investigation%20would%20be%20inappropriate%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cconsidering%20the%20exigencies%20of%20the%20investigation%20and%20the%20varying%20degrees%20of%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20data%20and%20the%20stage%20of%20investigation%20which%20may%20arise%20in%20each%20case.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20October%2C%20a%20Delhi%20court%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdevice-journalists-seized-press-freedom-delhi-court-the-wire%5C%22%3Eruled%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20case%20concerning%20the%20Delhi%20Police%E2%80%99s%20seizure%20of%20devices%20belonging%20to%20the%20editors%20and%20a%20manager%20of%20this%20news%20portal%2C%20that%20there%20was%20no%20reasonable%20ground%20to%20retain%20them%20since%20they%20had%20been%20in%20the%20possession%20of%20the%20police%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%20and%20mirror%20images%20of%20the%20material%20deemed%20important%20already%20exist.%20It%20is%20to%20be%20hoped%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20follows%20the%20lead%20of%20the%20junior%20court%20and%20firmly%20lays%20down%20the%20need%20for%20such%20guidelines.%20This%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20media%20freedom%2C%20academic%20freedom%2C%20and%20personal%20freedom.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EReaders%20write%20in%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDoes%20Israel%20have%20a%20choice%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPramod%20Thanedar%20writes%20in%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CGreetings.%20I%20understand%20your%20defense%20of%20Palestinians%20but%20not%20Hamas.%20You%20ought%20to%20read%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20charter%20which%20calls%20for%20the%20total%20destruction%20of%20the%20state%20of%20Israel.%20Obviously%2C%20I%20presume%20that%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20charter%20is%20not%20acceptable%20to%20you%20but%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20mention%20it%20in%20your%20article%3F%20At%20least%2C%20Israel%20is%20accountable%20for%20its%20excesses%20but%20Hamas%20is%20an%20unelected%20body%20that%20is%20not%20accountable%20to%20anyone.%20What%20choice%20does%20Israel%20have%20but%20to%20destroy%20it%20since%20Hamas%20started%20this%20round%20of%20violence%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EMy%20response%3A%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Thank%20you%20for%20your%20mail.%20I%20have%20never%20defended%20Hamas%20in%20my%20columns.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20my%20column%20of%20October%2028%2C%20I%20specifically%20recognised%20its%20October%207%20attacks%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecrime%20against%20humanity.%E2%80%9D%20We%20can%20agree%20that%20Hamas%20is%20a%20religious%20fundamentalist%20group%20that%20supports%20violent%20resistance%20to%20Israeli%20occupation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20question%2C%20Mr%20Thanedar%2C%20is%20how%20did%20Hamas%20itself%20come%20into%20being%3F%20A%20brief%20answer%20should%20surely%20take%20into%20consideration%20the%20forced%20expulsion%20of%20Palestinians%20and%20the%20capture%20of%20their%20land%20by%20Israeli%20Zionists%20supported%20by%20Western%20powers%3F%20Wouldn%E2%80%99t%20it%20also%20take%20into%20consideration%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20Israel%20evolved%20into%20a%20settler%20colonial%20apartheid%20state%3F%20Shouldn%E2%80%99t%20we%20also%20understand%20the%20decline%20and%20lack%20of%20credibility%20of%20Fatah%2C%20the%20political%20wing%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20that%20was%20secular%20but%20which%20was%20perceived%20to%20have%20become%20%E2%80%9Csoft%E2%80%9D%20in%20its%20resistance%20to%20Israel%3F%20It%20is%20this%20that%20saw%20Hamas%20win%20the%20election%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20legislature%20in%202006.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlease%20don%E2%80%99t%20frame%20Hamas%20and%20the%20mighty%20armed%20Israel%20state%20as%20binaries.%20The%20difference%20between%20them%20in%20terms%20of%20military%20power%20and%20political%20clout%20is%20immeasurable.%20It%20is%20also%20contestable%20that%20Hamas%20started%20this%20round%20of%20violence.%20Violence%20by%20Israel%20has%20been%20continuous%20over%20years%20because%2C%20ultimately%2C%20it%20has%20been%20illegally%20occupying%20Palestinian%20land.%20Also%2C%20finally%2C%20you%20cannot%20collapse%20the%20need%20to%20fight%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20armed%20wing%20with%20the%20killing%20of%20hundreds%20and%20thousands%20of%20ordinary%20Gazans.%C2%A0%20Israel%20always%20had%20a%20choice%3A%20it%20could%20have%20ended%20its%20illegal%20takeover%20of%20the%20Occupied%20Territories.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EGo%20back%20to%20the%20paper%20ballot%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERaja%20Sekhar%20made%20the%20following%20comments%20on%20the%20recently%20concluded%20assembly%20polls%20in%20a%20mail%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20have%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%2C%20anything%20is%20possible.%20I%20went%20through%20published%20information%20on%20the%20possibility%20of%20frauds%20in%20our%20election%20system.%20From%20now%20onwards%2C%20at%20least%2C%20we%20should%20work%20towards%20%E2%80%98real%20democracy%E2%80%99%20by%20ensuring%20that%20each%20vote%20is%20%E2%80%98recorded%20as%20cast%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98counted%20as%20recorded%E2%80%99%20to%20protect%20our%20India%E2%80%99s%20Republic%2C%20its%20independent%20judiciary%20and%20its%20existing%20Constitution.%20Here%20I%20would%20like%20to%20refer%20to%20what%20we%20should%20do%20to%20avoid%20the%20predictions%20of%20%E2%80%98future%20worst%20consequences%2C%20that%20may%20probably%20come%20if%20the%20RSS%20of%20BJP%20continues%20in%20power%20to%20rule%20India%E2%80%99%20as%20Dr.%20Parakala%20Prabhakar%20put%20it%20in%20his%20speeches.%20He%20argues%20that%20there%20is%20an%20urgent%20need%20that%20we%20get%20back%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Conly%20full%20100%25%20transparent%20and%20genuine%20mode%20of%20elections%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20through%20the%20ballot%20paper%20voting%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09194755%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-7.39.03%25E2%2580%25AFPM_cleanup-1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09194755%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-7.39.03%25E2%2580%25AFPM_cleanup-1.png%20720w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09194755%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-7.39.03%25E2%2580%25AFPM_cleanup-1-300x120.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684361%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22288%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EModern-day%20slavery%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELaw%20Students%20of%20Mumbai%20wrote%20us%20this%20interesting%20collective%20letter.%20We%20are%20publishing%20excerpts%20from%20it%20because%20the%20general%20view%20is%20that%20young%20Indians%20rarely%20find%20the%20time%20or%20inclination%20to%20involve%20themselves%20in%20issues%20of%20social%20concern.%20This%20letter%20is%20evidence%20that%20this%20may%20not%20always%20be%20the%20case%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20the%20concerned%20students%20of%20MNLU%20Mumbai%20are%20writing%20this%20letter%20to%20you%20with%20great%20pain%E2%80%A6It%20has%20come%20to%20our%20notice%20that%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%20of%20MNLU%20Mumbai%E2%80%A6recently%20terminated%20the%20employment%20of%20a%20driver%E2%80%A6solely%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20his%20refusal%20to%20undertake%20duties%20that%20were%20not%20part%20of%20his%20job%20description%2C%20ie%2C%20clean%20his%20home%2C%20kitchen%20utensils%20and%20toilet.%20When%20he%20objected%20to%20being%20asked%20to%20the%20clean%20the%20personal%20toilet%20of%20the%20VC%20at%20his%20personal%20residence%20in%20Pune%2C%20his%20services%20were%20terminated.%20What%20is%20particularly%20alarming%20in%20this%20case%20is%20that%20the%20driver%20belongs%20to%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%E2%80%A6%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20practice%20violates%20the%20principles%20of%20equality%20and%20justice%20enshrined%20in%20our%20Constitution.%20The%20concerned%20VC%20claims%20to%20be%20a%20teacher%20of%20constitutional%20law%20teacher%20and%20yet%20his%20actions%20go%20against%20the%20very%20ethos%20of%20what%20he%20preaches.%20Such%20a%20practice%20is%20also%20indicative%20of%20a%20form%20of%20modern%20slavery%20where%20individuals%20are%20coerced%20into%20performing%20tasks%20outside%20the%20scope%20of%20their%20employment%2C%20violating%20their%20dignity%20and%20perpetuating%20a%20system%20of%20discrimination%20based%20on%20caste%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20humbly%20request%20your%20institution%20to%20investigate%20this%20matter%20thoroughly%E2%80%A6the%20students%20will%20ensure%20that%20all%20the%20victims%20will%20come%20and%20give%20evidence%2C%20if%20required%E2%80%A6There%20are%20an%20estimated%2018.3%20million%20people%20in%20India%20forced%20into%20forms%20of%20modern%20slavery%20(about%2039%25%20of%20the%20world%20average).%20No%20NLU%20should%20be%20a%20forum%20where%20such%20practices%20carry%20on%20unchecked%E2%80%A6We%20end%20with%20the%20words%20of%20Martin%20Luther%20King%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EInjustice%20Anywhere%20Is%20a%20Threat%20To%20Justice%20Everywhere.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWrite%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eombudsperson%40thewire.in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702111512000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F03190918%2FScreenshot-2022-02-03-at-7.09.01-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-polls-verdicts-media-narratives-counting-day%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20fortnightly%20column%20from%20The%20Wire's%20ombudsperson.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-polls-verdicts-media-narratives-counting-day%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hadiya%20Denies%20Father's%20Fresh%20Claims%20That%20She%20Is%20Under%20'Illegal%20Detention'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F09131436%2FHadiya.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Hadiya%2C%20the%20Kerala%20woman%20whose%20conversion%20to%20Islam%20and%20marriage%20to%20a%20Muslim%20man%20resulted%20in%20a%20landmark%20ruling%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20about%20the%20autonomy%20of%20adult%20women%2C%20has%20denied%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20fresh%20allegation%20that%20she%20is%20under%20illegal%20detention%20by%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fthiruvananthapuram%2Fhadiya-kerala-conversion-marriage-9060979%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0the%20homeopathy%20doctor%20said%20in%20a%20video%20on%20Saturday%20that%20she%20has%20separated%20from%20her%20first%20husband%20Shafin%20Jahan%20and%20has%20remarried.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Constitution%20has%20given%20the%20right%20for%20every%20person%20to%20enter%20into%20marriage%20and%20get%20out%20of%20the%20relationship.%20It%20is%20a%20common%20thing%20in%20society.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20society%20is%20getting%20irritated%20in%20my%20case.%20I%20am%20a%20grown-up%20who%20is%20capable%20of%20making%20decisions.%20When%20I%20could%20not%20continue%20the%20marriage%20(with%20Jahan)%2C%20I%20got%20out%20of%20it.%20Now%2C%20I%20have%20married%20another%20person%20of%20my%20choice.%20I%20am%20happy%20and%20living%20as%20a%20Muslim.%20My%20parents%20are%20also%20aware%20about%20the%20remarriage%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20was%20released%20a%20day%20after%20her%20father%20K.M.%20Ashokan%20moved%20a%20habeas%20corpus%20petition%20in%20the%20Kerala%20high%20court%20alleging%20that%20he%20could%20not%20reach%20Hadiya%20over%20the%20phone%20and%20her%20homeopathy%20clinic%20was%20shut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Hadiya%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20she%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know%20why%20her%20father%20moved%20the%20high%20court.%20She%20did%20not%20disclose%20details%20of%20her%20new%20partner%2C%20saying%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20make%20them%20public.%20She%20has%20moved%20to%20Thiruvananthapuram%20from%20Mallapuram%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fhadiyas-father-moves-court-again-this-time-alleging-illegal-detention-101702061000388.html%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20said%20her%20%E2%80%9Cfather%20has%20created%20troubles%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20live.%20There%20have%20been%20cyberattacks%20on%20me%20which%20has%20made%20my%20life%20difficult.%20My%20father%20has%20always%20been%20made%20a%20tool%20by%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20forces.%20It%20is%20sad%20that%20he%20is%20allowing%20himself%20to%20be%20used%20that%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHadiya%20also%20denied%20the%20claims%20that%20her%20phone%20was%20switched%20off%2C%20stating%20instead%20that%20she%20was%20%E2%80%9Cin%20constant%20touch%20with%20her%20parents%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20remarried%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20subject%20of%20discussion%20again.%20I%20am%20a%20mature%20adult%20who%20is%20capable%20of%20taking%20her%20own%20decisions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackground%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20into%20a%20Hindu%20family%20in%20Kottayam%2C%20Hadiya%20said%20she%20was%20drawn%20to%20Islam%20when%20studying%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20She%20converted%20to%20that%20faith%20and%20married%20Jahan.%20Her%20father%20filed%20a%20habeas%20corpus%20plea%20in%202016%2C%20challenging%20the%20marriage.%20The%20high%20court%20nullified%20the%20marriage%20and%20ordered%20her%20to%20be%20placed%20in%20the%20protective%20custody%20of%20her%20Hindu%20parents%20or%20an%20institution%2C%20so%20that%20she%20is%20%E2%80%9Cprevented%20from%20being%20a%20further%20victim%20of%20%3Cem%3Elove%20jihad%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%20The%20judgment%20was%20perhaps%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20constitutional%20court%20used%20this%20term%2C%20a%20conspiracy%20theory%20that%20claims%20there%20is%20a%20plot%20to%20convert%20Hindu%20women%20to%20Islam%20through%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20March%202018%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-sets-aside-kerala-hc-order-annulling-hadiya-marriage%5C%22%3Erestored%3C%2Fa%3E%20her%20marriage%20and%20allowed%20her%20to%20live%20with%20her%20husband%20Jahan.%C2%A0The%20top%20court%20allowed%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20to%20probe%20the%20incident%20to%20see%20if%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20convert%20to%20Islam.%20The%20agency%20later%20closed%20the%20case%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnia-love-jihad-kerala-hadiya%5C%22%3Efinding%20no%20evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20support%20such%20a%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702108801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F09131436%2FHadiya.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhadiya-father-claim-illegal-detention-deny%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Kerala%20woman's%20conversion%20to%20Islam%20and%20subsequent%20marriage%20to%20a%20Muslim%20man%20resulted%20in%20a%20landmark%20ruling%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20about%20the%20autonomy%20of%20adult%20women.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhadiya-father-claim-illegal-detention-deny%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Economic%20Slowdown%20Affects%20Placements%20at%20IITs%2C%20Hiring%20Declines%20by%2015%25%20to%2030%25%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F09130925%2FEffect-21.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20economic%20slowdown%20being%20witnessed%20across%20the%20world%20has%20also%20come%20to%20affect%20recruitment%20even%20at%20the%20prestigious%20Indian%20Institutes%20of%20Technology%20(IITs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fjobs%2Ffresher%2Fconcerns-rise-as-final-placements-at-iits-show-15-30-decline-in-job-offers-for-class-of-2024%2Farticleshow%2F105847204.cms%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20hiring%20at%20IITs%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20final%20placement%20week%20which%20began%20on%20December%201%20%E2%80%93%20has%20declined%20by%20anywhere%20between%2015%25%20and%2030%25%20compared%20to%20previous%20years.%20Even%20after%20a%20week%20of%20the%20placement%20drive%20has%20passed%2C%20most%20students%20are%20yet%20to%20land%20a%20job%2C%20and%20the%20situation%20ahead%20looks%20bleak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20even%20students%20from%20the%20Computer%20Science%20stream%2C%20who%20would%20have%20usually%20received%20multiple%20job%20offers%2C%20are%20struggling%20to%20get%20even%20a%20single%20offer.%20%E2%80%9CRecruiters%20who%20used%20to%20hire%208-10%20students%20are%20now%20taking%201-2%20students%20each%3B%20some%20are%20coming%20to%20campus%20but%20leaving%20without%20recruiting%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20student%20at%20IIT-Kharagpur%20told%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gloomy%20scenario%20is%20attributable%20to%20the%20slowdown%20being%20witnessed%20across%20multiple%20sectors%2C%20including%20tech%2C%20consulting%2C%20and%20other%20services%20sectors.%20Economic%20shifts%2C%20geopolitical%20economic%20worries%2C%20and%20recession%20fears%20have%20resulted%20in%20the%20slowdown%20globally.%20The%20current%20slowdown%2C%20which%20is%20being%20witnessed%20specifically%20in%20the%20information%20technology%20(IT)%20sector%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20drag%20on%20for%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20quarters%2C%20Sekhar%20Garisa%2C%20CEO%20of%20job%20portal%20Foundit%20(formerly%20Monster)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fit-hiring-slowdown-to-continue-for-2-3-quarters-global-slowdown-to-blame-123112900556_1.html%5C%22%3Ehad%20told%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tide%20over%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20IT%20sector%2C%20%E2%80%9Cnon-tech%20sectors%20such%20as%20automobile%2C%20retail%2C%20and%20banking%20will%20be%20the%20saviours%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20tech%20talent%20as%20the%20traditional%20haven%20IT%20sector%20reduces%20hiring%20significantly%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%20Businessline%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Finfo-tech%2Ftech-talent-finds-new-haven-in-non-tech-sectors-amid-it-hiring-slowdown%2Farticle67462067.ece%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20also%20concerning%20at%20older%20IITs%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Bombay%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20Madras%2C%20Kharagpur%2C%20Roorkee%2C%20Guwahati%20and%20Varanasi%20(BHU).%20Of%20the%20total%2023%20IITs%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20older%20IITs%20are%20more%20prestigious%20than%20others%2C%20and%20it%20is%20extremely%20competitive%20to%20secure%20a%20seat%20in%20one%20of%20these%20institutes.%20As%20they%20attract%20the%20%3Cem%3Ecr%C3%A8me%20de%20