%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20aim%20to%20establish%20a%20circular%20economy%20where%20toys%20are%20reused%20repeatedly.%20This%20not%20only%20cuts%20costs%20but%20also%20benefits%20the%20environment.%20Considering%20how%20quickly%20kids%20outgrow%20things%2C%20toys%20often%20end%20up%20in%20landfills%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPocket-friendly%20for%20parents%20and%20fun%20for%20kids%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20habit%20of%20reusing%20and%20thrifting%20might%20have%20started%20trending%20recently%2C%20if%20we%20look%20back%20to%20our%20childhood%2C%20sharing%20children%E2%80%99s%20belongings%20has%20always%20been%20part%20of%20our%20culture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20pass%20down%20our%20toys%20and%20clothes%20to%20our%3Cem%3E%20chachi%2C%20mami%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20(aunts)%20kids.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20nuclear%20family%20setup%2C%20this%20trend%20has%20declined.%20I%20think%20it%20was%20this%20practice%20that%20has%20made%20people%20place%20their%20trust%20in%20us%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20initial%20reaction%20of%20the%20people%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20parents%20were%20very%20delighted%20and%20showed%20encouragement.%20While%20they%20were%20a%20little%20sceptical%20of%20sanitation%20since%20these%20products%20will%20be%20reused%2C%20I%20explained%20that%20we%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F115268%2Fbaghuwar-village-madhya-pradesh-sanitation-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esanitation%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20every%20toy%20that%20reaches%20their%20kid%20is%20safe%20for%20consumption%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetteri